1
00:00:47,440 --> 00:00:48,170
Did you hear?

2
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:49,480
Jiang got locked up.

3
00:00:49,480 --> 00:00:50,160
That's a good thing.

4
00:00:50,160 --> 00:00:51,120
Let's drink to that.

5
00:00:51,120 --> 00:00:51,800
He deserved it.

6
00:00:51,800 --> 00:00:52,400
Alright.

7
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:54,120
Let me say a few words.

8
00:00:56,200 --> 00:00:57,130
This first drink

9
00:00:57,440 --> 00:00:59,570
is to celebrate winning second place.

10
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:01,360
Happy second place!

11
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:09,100
And for this second drink,

12
00:01:09,720 --> 00:01:10,520
let's

13
00:01:11,039 --> 00:01:12,160
send off Liu Ma.

14
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:14,960
Come on.

15
00:01:16,320 --> 00:01:16,920
Come on.

16
00:01:17,440 --> 00:01:18,120
Bottoms up.

17
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:25,760
Liu Ma.

18
00:01:27,440 --> 00:01:28,770
Are you really leaving?

19
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,039
I don't want to.

20
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:32,840
I love this place's

21
00:01:33,080 --> 00:01:34,800
passion and authenticity.

22
00:01:35,720 --> 00:01:37,160
But I have to face reality.

23
00:01:37,160 --> 00:01:38,080
Actually,

24
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:39,400
you could stay.

25
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:41,930
We could open a music classroom together.

26
00:01:42,039 --> 00:01:43,370
The children in Lincang

27
00:01:43,479 --> 00:01:45,009
need more music education.

28
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:47,080
Sure.

29
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,289
I'll invest.

30
00:01:48,479 --> 00:01:49,680
Opening a bar works too.

31
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,720
I'll be the resident singer,

32
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:51,400
and I'll manage it.

33
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,200
How much are you paying me?

34
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,200
Here.

35
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:56,060
To celebrate your successful performance,

36
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,720
I made you some extra dishes.

37
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,600
Thank you, Uncle and Auntie. Your hand hasn't healed yet.

38
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:00,520
Over here.

39
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:02,850
Enjoy your meal.

40
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:04,360
Mom.

41
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,280
What is this?

42
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,080
I added some dragon fruit just for you.

43
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:08,600
It's a new dish.

44
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:10,400
Try it and give us some feedback.

45
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,160
Boss,

46
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:14,120
another bottle of homemade liquor.

47
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,050
Coming right up.

48
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,680
Uncle.

49
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,600
Ma'er.

50
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:21,680
Uncle.

51
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:23,400
you...

52
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:24,490
why are you here?

53
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:26,200
Are you okay?

54
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:27,079
No, I'm fine.

55
00:02:27,079 --> 00:02:28,280
Did they hurt you?

56
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,570
Did they beat you silly?

57
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:33,440
Are you drunk?

58
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:34,640
No, no.

59
00:02:34,920 --> 00:02:35,800
This is my uncle.

60
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:36,520
I'm fine.

61
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:37,200
I'm not drunk.

62
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:37,600
Come on.

63
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,920
I'm not drunk at all.

64
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:40,579
My uncle is definitely drunk.

65
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,560
Are these your friends?

66
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,890
They're all my friends.

67
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:45,480
Hello, everyone.

68
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:46,560
Ma'er.

69
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:48,560
No wonder you like coming to Lincang.

70
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:50,020
It's great here, isn't it?

71
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,329
I'm telling you,

72
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,400
I've been here for three days,

73
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:55,329
and I've been drunk for three days.

74
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,160
I know.

75
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,620
I know perfectly well.

76
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,240
Ma'er.

77
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:03,480
I've decided.

78
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,440
I'll stay here and learn

79
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:07,370
to cook authentic Lincang dishes.

80
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,480
When I go back,

81
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:11,640
I'll open a Lincang restaurant too.

82
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:17,020
I made a fool of myself.

83
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:18,579
I can't hold my liquor.

84
00:03:23,079 --> 00:03:25,320
Even though our band didn't win the championship,

85
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:26,800
we're still together.

86
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:30,240
Jiang used public opinion to stir up trouble,

87
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,200
and hit someone.

88
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:33,020
The police found out about it.

89
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:35,560
He couldn't understand why the online buzz

90
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:37,360
didn't affect the competition.

91
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:39,040
It's because he doesn't get it.

92
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:39,720
Here.

93
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,480
We believe what we see,

94
00:03:41,720 --> 00:03:42,960
what we hear,

95
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:45,290
and we trust the people we live with

96
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:47,200
and strive for our dreams with.

97
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:58,520
Look.

98
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:03,800
Wildfire Club.

99
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,320
You've got guts.

100
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:26,020
Aren't you afraid Auntie will scold you?

101
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:31,800
Is Uncle awake?

102
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:33,560
He's been awake for a while.

103
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:35,360
He even transferred money to me.

104
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,380
Where did he get the money?

105
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,880
The loan shark gangs got busted.

106
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:41,800
We got the interest back.

107
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,740
It's just like he said.

108
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:46,840
Your luck turns eventually.

109
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:48,880
Then...

110
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,400
Brother.

111
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,880
Can you stay a little longer?

112
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,080
I...

113
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:11,360
Anan.

114
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:12,920
Anan.

115
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:15,600
What is it?

116
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,240
What is it?

117
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:24,960
Dear Wildfire Club,

118
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:27,000
after a decision by the organizers,

119
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,160
we sincerely invite you

120
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:30,360
to participate as a guest performer

121
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:33,080
in this year's Wild Grass Music Festival.

122
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:36,010
Participating as a guest in the formal performance.

123
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:38,440
Bro.

124
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:41,810
Can we really go to the music festival?

125
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:43,320
We've made it.

126
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:51,960
That's great.

127
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:53,760
Don't.

128
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:56,080
I'm going to tell Qiuqiu.

129
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,880
Tell her you like her first.

130
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,520
Qiuqiu.

131
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:44,080
Okay, that's all for today.

132
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:45,080
Class dismissed.

133
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:48,120
Goodbye.

134
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:56,760
Our band

135
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,840
has been invited to perform at the music festival.

136
00:06:58,840 --> 00:06:59,600
Really?

137
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:01,640
Hurry. Liu Ma is waiting for us in the rehearsal room.

138
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:02,240
Let's go.

139
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:30,160
Liu Ma.

140
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:32,280
The music festival.

141
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:33,560
Are you going?

142
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:34,680
I'm going.

143
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,170
I'll be right there.

144
00:07:57,960 --> 00:07:58,600
Bro.

145
00:07:58,960 --> 00:07:59,760
This time,

146
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:01,730
let's go on stage together.

147
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:06,890
Let's go on stage together.

148
00:08:10,880 --> 00:08:11,520
Let's go.
